%% Sequence Diagram - Order Query (INT-003)
%% Data: 2026-07-23 (revisão corretiva)
%% Intent: INT-003 (Consultar pedido por número)
%% Fluxo: API_ONLY — sem LLM, template determinístico

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant MARH as API MARH
    participant Lambda as Lambda Agent
    participant Secrets as Secrets Manager
    participant Orch as ma-hr-orch
    participant CW as CloudWatch
    participant XR as X-Ray

    Note over MARH,XR: INT-003: "Consultar pedido PEDIDO-SINTETICO-001."

    MARH->>Lambda: InvokeFunction (AWS SDK)<br/>{"message": "Consultar pedido PEDIDO-SINTETICO-001.",<br/>"company_id": "uuid-empresa-selecionada",<br/>"user_id": "uuid-usuario"}
    activate Lambda

    Lambda->>XR: Begin trace segment
    Lambda->>CW: Log: request_received, correlation_id=uuid-123

    %% Context validation
    Lambda->>Lambda: validate_context(payload)
    Note over Lambda: company_id presente e válido<br/>Empresa NÃO pode ser alterada pelo chat

    %% Classification
    Lambda->>Lambda: classify_deterministic("Consultar pedido PEDIDO-SINTETICO-001.")
    Note over Lambda: Pattern: "pedido" + número<br/>→ INT-003 (Consultar pedido por número)<br/>→ flow=API_ONLY<br/>→ endpoint=GET /v1/orders/{orderNumber}

    Lambda->>CW: Log: intent=INT-003, flow=API_ONLY

    %% Extract order number (deterministic)
    Lambda->>Lambda: extract_order_number("PEDIDO-SINTETICO-001.")
    Note over Lambda: orderNumber = "PEDIDO-SINTETICO-001"<br/>Nunca inventado pelo modelo

    %% Get credentials if needed
    Lambda->>Secrets: GetSecretValue("marh-agent/ma-hr-orch-token")
    activate Secrets
    Secrets-->>Lambda: token (cached in Lambda lifecycle)
    deactivate Secrets

    %% Call ma-hr-orch
    Lambda->>Orch: GET /v1/orders/PEDIDO-SINTETICO-001<br/>Headers: Authorization token<br/>Timeout: connect=3s read=8s
    activate Orch

    Note over Orch: Processa consulta...<br/>Valida: token, interlocutor, FNP, prova de vida

    Orch-->>Lambda: 200 OK<br/>{"orderNumber": "PEDIDO-SINTETICO-001",<br/>"status": "PAID",<br/>"orderDate": "2026-07-10",<br/>"totalOrder": 5000.00,<br/>"productInfo": {"productName": "Vale Alimentação"},<br/>"paymentMethod": "BOLETO",<br/>"steps": [...],<br/>"billingDocumentNumber": "...",<br/>"contractNumber": "..."}
    deactivate Orch

    Lambda->>CW: Log: ma_hr_orch_success, duration_ms=1200, http_status=200

    %% Schema validation + Allowlist (no LLM)
    Lambda->>Lambda: validate_schema(response)
    Lambda->>Lambda: apply_allowlist("order_detail", response)
    Note over Lambda: PERMITIDOS: orderNumber, status, orderDate,<br/>totalOrder, productInfo.productName,<br/>paymentMethod, steps<br/>REMOVIDOS: billingDocumentNumber,<br/>contractNumber, idLegalPersonBilling

    %% Complementary sanitization
    Lambda->>Lambda: sanitize_complementary(allowed_fields)

    %% Deterministic template (no LLM)
    Lambda->>Lambda: render_template("order_detail", sanitized_data)
    Note over Lambda: Traduz status: PAID → "Pagamento confirmado"<br/>Template determinístico — sem LLM

    %% Output validation
    Lambda->>Lambda: validate_output(response)
    Note over Lambda: Re-scan PII<br/>Tamanho OK

    Lambda->>CW: Log: request_complete, total_duration_ms=1250, status=success
    Lambda->>XR: End trace segment

    Lambda-->>MARH: 200 OK<br/>{"response": "Pedido PEDIDO-SINTETICO-001\nStatus: Pagamento confirmado\nData: 10/07/2026\nProduto: Vale Alimentação\nValor: R$ 5.000,00\nForma de pagamento: Boleto",<br/>"intent": "INT-003",<br/>"flow": "API_ONLY"}
    deactivate Lambda

    Note over MARH,XR: Latência estimada: ~1.3s<br/>LLM: zero chamadas<br/>PII não exposto
